{"tid":1387954,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣］反送中通識教材；個人成長與人際關係/今日香港 /現代中國 /全球化","createTime":"2019-07-30T15:32:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T03:43:55.000Z","uid":268410,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1b4b334b3ead32eeff379ab71dc387ab3303e706","tid":1387954,"uid":268410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:32:03.000Z","msg":"Sorry for 1999<br />\n今日仲有人覺得政治唔關我事 同身邊既港豬媽媽 <br />\n唔理發生咩事，我成日諗 你而家唔理政治 但你仔女會受返,同埋你咁緊張d仔女功課，通識會教嫁喎，你點幫佢溫書，數落「反送中」已橫跨四個單元；<br />\n<br />\n個人成長與人際關係 <br />\n<br />\n今日香港<br />\n<br />\n現代中國<br />\n<br />\n全球化<br />\n<br />\n反送中係香港重要既歷史，我都幾肯定未來幾年反送中會不停係教科書出現，再要講落去 我覺得化學 經濟 英文科都關事 。<br />\n<br />\n我地可唔可以從教材入手 去引導覺得政治唔關我事既人<br />\n包含多d通識詞彙 ，可能整埋模擬試題 <br />\n<br />\n有冇學校已經做緊？分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f15aaf85715a50684f1a576862c2f9d907dfe9e","tid":1387954,"uid":268410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:42:47.000Z","msg":"Why負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafd9e663c654b93d6e698d73737616d9f1c2ac0","tid":1387954,"uid":268410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:43:16.000Z","msg":"死港豬 dllm<br />\n你仔女有排受呀"},{"pid":"ee611496890225551c0a208b51a30ab364898693","tid":1387954,"uid":21501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:50:04.000Z","msg":"有無16年dse及之後嘅人讀本通識書有講雨傘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6d140c0f04a9f6bf8c1ef0d0fa4e9534e07045","tid":1387954,"uid":208088,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ee611496890225551c0a208b51a30ab364898693","tid":1387954,"uid":21501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:50:04.000Z","msg":"有無16年dse及之後嘅人讀本通識書有講雨傘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:52:03.000Z","msg":"印象中無講 但老師會自己印notes"},{"pid":"9d09b903c3c35a07396533